high_descs: Turn around and face the coffee maker.
Pick up the mug from the coffee maker.
Turn right and carry the mug to the microwave over the sink.
Put the mug in the microwave and turn it on.
Take the mug out of the microwave, turn left and carry the mug to the coffee maker.
Put the mug back on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Heat a mug in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the coffee machine.
Pick up the mug from the machine.
Head right and bring the mug to the coffee machine.
Heat the mug in the microwave.
Bring the mug back to the coffee machine.
Place the mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug on the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn around and walk down to the coffee maker
Pick up the dark mug from the coffee maker
Turn right and walk a few feet down to the microwave above the sink
Heat the mug in the microwave and remove it
Turn left and go back to the coffee maker
Put the mug in the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the heated mug in the coffee maker
